{"tid":1654732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"極重要 發現有人借光復逐家逐戶敲門要錢","createTime":"2019-10-14T17:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T17:53:56.000Z","uid":267428,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eb9d9ef57e1157a82f9368f681b2e5a10edb1991","tid":1654732,"uid":267428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:32:50.000Z","msg":"今日同個Uncle食開飯<br />\n<br />\n佢本身黃但係屬於50 60歲嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n講起佢話前幾日有人上門敲門<br />\n<br />\n話要收咩光復費用 叫佢捐錢<br />\n<br />\n佢本身就係黃再加上俾人講多兩句又唔好意思拒絕<br />\n<br />\n最後攞咗$200比佢哋<br />\n<br />\n真人真事 一手料<br />\n<br />\n難聽啲講 完全同警訊嘅畫面一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n如果下次真係有人遇到唔好留手 直接私了 呢一種人比臥底狗更加可恥 <br />\n<br />\n但如果真係自己手足做嘅麻煩你唔好再咁做<br />\n<br />\n你要錢嘅唔該出聲而唔係咁樣要人捐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以嘅麻煩民間記者會澄清番我哋絕對唔會咁樣收錢"},{"pid":"7c3cb27d114a2d14fc90df5b56b84827ef301cfb","tid":1654732,"uid":129269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:34:19.000Z","msg":"[尋求真相] 推到有HKDI既知情人篤灰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654688</a>"},{"pid":"940af831ee6b5cf6e18ee43cb4ccd2c4f4fc3885","tid":1654732,"uid":5701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:35:02.000Z","msg":"唔信係自己人做<br />\n不過覺得民間記者會應該幫手割<br />\n(擺明唔係同路人)"},{"pid":"8d3fd392926685ff1204bfdf2e69adb34920c330","tid":1654732,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845e650e3624028461831aa5613679f6063024e0","tid":1654732,"uid":314021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:35:26.000Z","msg":"下次 影大頭 報上tg 萬事小心 呢班一定係休班狗黎"},{"pid":"933fcb00c0f13e4b0d2290f0a91ec948c784f833","tid":1654732,"uid":94088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:39:25.000Z","msg":"純文字討論呀？<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"b215ed22def4ca4b2d18b8cf7369568431bc4d35","tid":1654732,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"